Title: An Act Changing the Name of the San Isidro Community School in Barangay San Isidro, Municipality of San Nicolas, Province of Pangasinan, to Bensican-San Isidro Community School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 839
An Act Changing the Name of the San Isidro Community School in Barangay San Isidro, Municipality of San Nicolas, Province of Pangasinan, to Bensican-San Isidro Community School
Section 1. The name of the San Isidro Community School in Barangay San Isidro, Municipality of San Nicolas, Province of Pangasinan, is hereby changed to Bensican-San Isidro Community School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1awp++i1
Approved: April 27, 1984
